about: My little sister Christy is a big ball of energy, very friendly,
and always willing to help a friend or family.
This is probably why she works at Sales Coordinator at Silver Cloud.
I love her even though we don’t always share the same interest
but it helps she eats the chicken feet while I help eat the leg and thigh. =)
She is my friend, who I can call to complain or celebrate about anything
and count on her support, strength and laughter.
